How to install 
=======================
Copy repository:
git init
git clone https://github.com/kempny/lcd44780
cd lcd44780

or 

copy lcdi2c.x.x.x.tgz
unpack: 
tar -xf lcdi2c.x.x.x.tgz
(change x.x.x to version number)
cd lcdi2c

make
make install
make clean

The library will be installed in:

/usr/local/lib

The header file in:

/usr/local/include


To uninstall library
=======================

make uninstall


To compile examples
======================

cd examples
make
